<h4 id="googlecloudrecaptchaenterprisev1testingoptionstestingchallenge">Google<wbr>Cloud<wbr>Recaptchaenterprise<wbr>V1Testing<wbr>Options<wbr>Testing<wbr>Challenge</h4>

{{% choosable language csharp %}}
<dl class="tabular"><dt>Testing<wbr>Challenge<wbr>Unspecified</dt>
    <dd>TESTING_CHALLENGE_UNSPECIFIED{{% md %}}Perform the normal risk analysis and return either nocaptcha or a challenge depending on risk and trust factors.{{% /md %}}</dd><dt>Nocaptcha</dt>
    <dd>NOCAPTCHA{{% md %}}Challenge requests for this key will always return a nocaptcha, which does not require a solution.{{% /md %}}</dd><dt>Unsolvable<wbr>Challenge</dt>
    <dd>UNSOLVABLE_CHALLENGE{{% md %}}Challenge requests for this key will always return an unsolvable challenge.{{% /md %}}</dd></dl>
{{% /choosable %}}

{{% choosable language go %}}
